{"type": "article", "id": 18578, "title": "对，我今天心情不好，我有 29 条理由丨好奇心研究所", "description": "根本不是我的错。", "date": "2015-12-05T16:40:43Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1062, "name": "情绪"}, {"id": 11405, "name": "好奇心研究所"}], "category": 3, "column": 33, "author": 130547, "comment_count": 22, "praise_count": 191, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607121148DCpy3JwKqlcVYI0L.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t1. 夏天，太热。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121133pV9WlsUwThGSqLiJ.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.75888325\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>2.</span>冬天，太冷。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121134IamxJz7HgNVic1Tj.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.48096192\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t3. 春<span>/</span>秋天，太困。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121135UrGKEBgJhpjZdMYw.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.512\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t4. 听说下周又雾霾。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121135Ub1LV0xwFkEnuZH9.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"1.54727273\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t5. 地铁太挤。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121136QZLBviOspnrFTzta.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.694\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t6. 跑着追公交，师傅不等我。 \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121137j6qVnoeH8FXclCi5.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.72596154\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t7. 叫滴滴附近有<span> 64 </span>辆车无人应答。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145608WIZVXpBHAw9TJNig.gif\" width=\"400\" height=\"325\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.8125\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t8. 叫  <span>Uber </span>此时段提价<span> 2 </span>倍。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121137Pwm2JsBoCykbL1ed.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t9. WIFI 太慢。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121138EnTLe6C2WJzwP97O.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.66869301\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t10. 网购失败。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121138uxigW7bwBpEHYTXC.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t11. 很多衣服没洗。 \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071211390YWuoShL3zBXNsIH.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.5859375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t12. 窗户外面好吵。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121139jelz1ntWLkoIqy6J.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.604\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t13. 整个电影院除了我都是情侣。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121140uaH2xr5CldiARFWc.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.424\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t14. 花 50 块看了一部烂片。 \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121140q1wEQNjKmflF7b6Z.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.426\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t15. 姨妈期。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071211419cVkb3oMBSlLu72U.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t16. 姨妈期不准。 \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145611mVaIBXl4yEhSHZdb.gif\" width=\"400\" height=\"300\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t17. 女朋友姨妈期。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121142c2sHRo9JENSCn8Ge.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t18. 老板处女座。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121143NydARzmKocYMfljS.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t19. 同事双鱼座。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121143lG5MUrP0g6aWZBJR.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.7475\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t20. 起太早。没睡好。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261456136SyXVAx0fU1rGbTW.gif\" width=\"245\" height=\"152\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.62040816\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t21. 晚上又加班。 \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071211443Hfiehmno6S5vrWI.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.75347222\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t22. 已经半夜 23 点 50 分，根本没玩够。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121145aIX4tj3zgT5DUECq.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t23. 我不想解释。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145615NPiH9LVfAhgr0vkp.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"238\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.476\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t24. 我只想静静。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145616tmfC8i6DwBjqWKoG.jpg\" width=\"625\" height=\"345\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.552\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t25. 你不理我！ \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121145GgsMdAxuwi4WPRNz.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.5637931\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t26. 越是亲近的人，越容易发脾气。<span>@Mars</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121146F2BRjSkUxMLgZXJG.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.84291188\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>27. 人品差到一定程度。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071211469WFMqINt8J6ZTj3a.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.70140281\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t28. 这世界怎么了<span>? </span>（<span>@ Nitaco</span>）\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121147beD40MTwiIjx8UWO.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.64692483\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t29. 好吧。今天就原谅我。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145617sP1gCUFK7GAZ8bxo.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"299\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.598\" data-format=\"gif\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><span><em>好奇心研究所的微博（@好奇心研究所）和微信公众号（ID：QLab42）全面上线啦，关注就可以与所长亲密接触。</em></span><em></em></span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n\n"}